com.menonvarun.test.automation.framework.keywordmodel.suite

Interface ISuiteFileReader

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CsvSuiteFileReader, ExcelSuiteFileReader

    public interface ISuiteFileReader
    An interface to represent the Suite file reader for reading and parsing the test-suite files.
    Author:
    Varun Menon

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean isSupported(File file)
      Methods to identify whether the said suite file is supported by the implementing class or not.
      List<ISimpleTest> read(File file, List<String> arguments)

    • Method Detail

      • isSupported

        boolean isSupported(File file)
        Methods to identify whether the said suite file is supported by the implementing class or not.
        Parameters:
        file - - File object of the test-suite file.
        Returns:
        true or false based on whether file is supported or not.

      • read

        List<ISimpleTest> read(File file,
                     List<String> arguments)
        Method to parse and return the test instances of the test present inside the said suite file.
        Parameters:
        file - File object of the test-suite file.
        arguments - - List of String required to read or parse the said test-suite file. These arguments are mainly related to the path of suite file, sheetname(in case of excel), delimiters (in case of csv), separators(in case of csv).
        Returns:
        List of ISimpleTest after parsing the test-suite file.
